#. <section class="sutta" id="sn37.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn37.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.14:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "1. Abbreviated Texts"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn37.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Pañcaverasutta"
msgstr "14. Five Threats"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn37.14:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo … pe … nirayaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"“Anuruddha, when females have five qualities, when their body breaks up, "
"after death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the "
"underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn37.14:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn37.14:1.3"
msgid ""
"Pāṇātipātī ca hoti, adinnādāyī ca hoti, kāmesumicchācārī ca hoti, musāvādī "
"ca hoti, surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhāyī ca hoti—"
msgstr ""
"They kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, and "
"consume alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "sn37.14:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, anuruddha, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā "
"paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When females have these five qualities, when their body breaks up, after "
"death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, "
"hell.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.14:1.5"
msgid "Cuddasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.14:1.6"
msgid "Paṭhamapeyyālavaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: puriso ca → dve manāpā amanāpā ca (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.1"
msgid "Mātugāmo puriso ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
#. VAR: tidhammo ca → āveṇiko tīhi dhammehi (bj) | āveṇikā tīhi anuruddho (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.2"
msgid "āveṇikā tidhammo ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.3"
msgid "Kodhano upanāhī ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.4"
msgid "issukī maccharena ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.5"
msgid "Aticārī ca dussīlo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.6"
msgid "appassuto ca kusīto;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.7"
msgid "Muṭṭhassati pañcaveraṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.8"
msgid "kaṇhapakkhe pakāsito."
msgstr ""
